headline: 3 Tobacco Stocks to Watch as Smoke-Free Trends Ignite Growth
summary: Tobacco industry leaders like PM, MO and BTI are investing heavily in smoke-free products to align with health trends and regulatory shifts. Despite declining cigarette sales, strong pricing power and RRP growth support a sustainable outlook.
